  "title": "Combining pkgutil and Typing for Production Code in Python 3.12+",
  "summary": "This guide demonstrates the effective utilization of pkgutil and Type Hints (typing) in Python 3.12+, enhancing maintainability and readability in production code.",

  "key_points": [
    "Utilize `pkgutil` to load modules dynamically",
